713,"uid":13466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T04:58:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/11/26/124419_0c9fe4c28802fc3283b2597eaa9bb0f8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F11%2F26%2F124419_0c9fe4c28802fc3283b2597eaa9bb0f8.jpg&h=5f799b4e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/11/26/124419_7cb73877e7d4e3f93b73f965f7f249ae.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F11%2F26%2F124419_7cb73877e7d4e3f93b73f965f7f249ae.jpg&h=d5fdede7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n送你幾件 慢慢奶</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n件肥熟女熟味夠，好肉，<br />\n坐上嚟搖，美極西汁燴巨龍，諗起都硬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c984e0ac957a9bf846b5db86e04e9b87e4fb4818","tid":1713,"uid":13466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T05:12:32.000Z","msg":"真心覺得，其實欣宜應該幾好砌。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/11/26/130207_67629d1b5890efbbc229cbe2a633ce1a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F11%2F26%2F130207_67629d1b5890efbbc229cbe2a633ce1a.jpg&h=9bb611d4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmSs6An6eTPnNzhmoMqAPP2TuAsRPuzFGK76XKTWNrwb26?filename=0Dic2A.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0Dic2A.jpg&h=ab1ef793&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n陽光氣息，大波，皮膚幾滑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/11/26/130251_318e4b5714e623f3ce7b163fd05be46e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F11%2F26%2F130251_318e4b5714e623f3ce7b163fd05be46e.jpg&h=93b74d8d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n西口西面咁<br />\n一邊騎住你喪搖，一邊星你兩巴，再屌鳩你：「唔准你咁快射呀，上次你4個字就出野，我邊夠喉呀？我未叫你射你咪撚射呀！」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmVAF16LDDtxqEQ29xLx2bWiNaAZYFgD6A1WjwFuAhRqtN?filename=UyztHh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUyztHh.jpg&h=4396a159&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n右邊幅圖，肥婆扑野最佳姿勢！<br />\n肥美肉脾晾喺我膊頭，我下插打樁機咁，一下大大力穿透佢塊濕立立、漲卜卜嘅黑皮肥西，d「噗滋噗滋」嘅水聲，加上同佢恥骨上肥厚脂肪碰撞下嘅「啪啪聲」，簡直係最完美嘅催情交響樂！<br />\n<br />\n如果佢隻腳板無洗仲正，<br />\n腳味+肥婆獨有嘅汗味mix埋，我再一口吮佢腳指、舔佢腳趾罅，諗起都壯陽呀！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3954d65830b9b4dcd50e86cc9fcae0325eb368ee","tid":1713,"uid":1517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T05:32:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>真心覺得，其實欣宜應該幾好砌。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/11/26/130207_67629d1b5890efbbc229cbe2a633ce1a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F11%2F26%2F130207_67629d1b5890efbbc229cbe2a633ce1a.jpg&h=e99837b3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmSs6An6eTPnNzhmoMqAPP2TuAsRPuzFGK76XKTWNrwb26?filename=0Dic2A.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0Dic2A.jpg&h=2dc50b0e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n陽光氣息，大波，皮膚幾滑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/11/26/130251_318e4b5714e623f3ce7b163fd05be46e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F11%2F26%2F130251_318e4b5714e623f3ce7b163fd05be46e.jpg&h=e1996bea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n西口西面咁<br />\n一邊騎住你喪搖，一邊星你兩巴，再屌鳩你：「唔准你咁快射呀，上次你4個字就出野，我邊夠喉呀？我未叫你射你咪撚射呀！」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmVAF16LDDtxqEQ29xLx2bWiNaAZYFgD6A1WjwFuAhRqtN?filename=UyztHh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUyztHh.jpg&h=c54d5dc4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n右邊幅圖，肥婆扑野最佳姿勢！<br />\n肥美肉脾晾喺我膊頭，我下插打樁機咁，一下大大力穿透佢塊濕立立、漲卜卜嘅黑皮肥西，d「噗滋噗滋」嘅水聲，加上同佢恥骨上肥厚脂肪碰撞下嘅「啪啪聲」，簡直係最完美嘅催情交響樂！<br />\n<br />\n如果佢隻腳板無洗仲正，<br />\n腳味+肥婆獨有嘅汗味mix埋，我再一口吮佢腳指、舔佢腳趾罅，諗起都壯陽呀！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n衰樣衰同份人小氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n屌不得 屌不得"},{"pid":"1e0e8fffd6894cbf49eb63084db69b283ca46081","tid":1713,"uid":1517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T05:33:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>真心覺得，其實欣宜應該幾好砌。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/11/26/130207_67629d1b5890efbbc229cbe2a633ce1a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F11%2F26%2F130207_67629d1b5890efbbc229cbe2a633ce1a.jpg&h=9bb611d4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmSs6An6eTPnNzhmoMqAPP2TuAsRPuzFGK76XKTWNrwb26?filename=0Dic2A.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0Dic2A.jpg&h=ab1ef793&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n陽光氣息，大波，皮膚幾滑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/11/26/130251_318e4b5714e623f3ce7b163fd05be46e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F11%2F26%2F130251_318e4b5714e623f3ce7b163fd05be46e.jpg&h=93b74d8d&s={SIZE}\" /><b